AUDIO: 'So, say you have some agent or model performing a task for you, but you want a different agent or model to audit it and to let deliver a report of findings back to the original agent, who then double-checks everything.'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'I think this is a fairly common workflow that many people may want to use, but when you\'re going across Claude Code or Codex or Hermes Agent, it can be a little tricky. So, in this video, I\'m going to show you step-by-step, and we\'re actually going'

[00:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'to create this kind of ultimate cross-agent workflow. So, that by the end of this video, you\'ll be able to set this up yourself. So, you\'ve seen me designing and going through multi-agent workflows before, and those were largely just in Hermes'

[00:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
